      "amount": "1 tablespoon, toasted"
    }
  ],
  "instructions": [
    "Toast pecans and cashews in a pan until lightly browned.",
    "In another pan, heat oil over medium-high heat. Add onions and bell pepper, sauté for about 5 minutes or until soft.",
    "Add ginger and cook for an additional minute. Stir in toasted pecans and cashews.",
    "Mix together palm sugar, soy sauce, and fish sauce in a small bowl. Pour this mixture into the pan with vegetables.",
    "Simmer for 3-4 minutes until the sauce thickens slightly. Stir in basil leaves and sesame seeds.",
    "Serve hot over steamed rice."
